Ε. Palogiannidi, E. Iosif, P. Koutsakis and A. Potamianos, “A Semantic-Affective Compositional Approach for the Affective Labelling of Adjective-Noun and Noun-Noun Pairs”, in Proc. of the 15th Annual Conference of the North American Chapter of the Association for Computational Linguistics: Human Language Technologies (NAACL HLT 2016), San Diego, USA.